Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Question}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.57,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Battling’s intense!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.57,0:00:06.99,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I’ll be giving today’s PokéProblem!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.70,0:00:12.95,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Which is the first Pokémon \N Professor Kukui sends out today?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.50,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Get the answer at the end of the episode!
Comment: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.75,0:00:20.79,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Satoshi has become the first-ever Champion \N of the Alola Pokémon League.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.09,0:00:24.09,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Now, Pikachu! Electric Net!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.34,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Lucario! Use Dragon Pulse!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.52,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Together with Royal Mask \N and his other friends,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.52,0:00:40.44,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,as well as Bebenom’s evolved form, Agoyon, \N Satoshi fought a full power battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! \N Let’s go, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.94,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Here we go, Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.45,0:00:53.66,Main,Satoshi & Kukui,0,0,0,,This is our full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.04,Main,Satoshi & Kukui,0,0,0,,Sparking Gigavolt!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.75,0:01:02.54,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Combining their strength, \N they finally managed to drive Akujiking away.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.25,0:01:04.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.71,0:01:05.96,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,You did it-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.09,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Royal Mask!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.60,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I should be the one \N thanking you, Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.65,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kukui’s in quite the bind!
Comment: 10,0:01:24.48,0:01:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 10,0:02:52.53,0:02:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.18,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Oh, um, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.60,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I’m sorry to have \N kept this from you for so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.89,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! \N No way, no way, no way, {\i1}no way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.48,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,He’s Royal... Royal is him...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.61,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Professor Kukui is Royal Mask...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.37,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.38,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I can’t wait for \N the exhibition match!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I mean, this is {\i1}so cool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.97,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It means I get to battle Royal Mask \N {\i1}and{\i0} the Professor, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.89,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Don’t you think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.02,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You have a point!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.56,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,All right! \N Let’s do this, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.27,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I’ll have the battlefield \N usable by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.86,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s do this, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.36,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Satoshi versus Professor Kukui...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.66,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,This’ll be the hottest battle \N in all of Alola!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.91,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Alolan Father and Son \N Showdown!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.91,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,We’ll all cheer you on!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.41,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,We couldn’t possibly {\i1}not{\i0} be \N excited about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.75,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi, let’s make tomorrow’s match \N a 6v6 full battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.26,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That means I can bring \N Agoyon too, right, Professor?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.26,0:04:39.63,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Of course! It’s part of our family, \N too, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.30,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.15,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hey, Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.44,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s do our best, together!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.87,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Let’s give it our full power \N tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.79,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.58,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enjoy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.79,0:05:20.09,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Yesterday’s award ceremony \N was full of surprises!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.59,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,I am safe! This is Jeekyo.{Ah, a line where we have a choice between an excessively early cut-off point and a scene-bleed. LOVELY. Opting for scene-bleed. -StarfishI think the bleed's entirely fine, especially since he has another line right after. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.59,0:05:27.60,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,I will be commenting on \N today’s event until the end!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.52,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,The Alola Pokémon League \N has been full of excitement.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.19,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi has been crowned \N its first-ever Champion!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.52,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,And the one waiting for \N this first-ever Champion is...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.53,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,...the ruler of the Royal Dome, \N Royal Mask!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.53,0:05:44.53,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,But, shockingly, it turns out \N his true identity was Professor Kukui!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.53,0:05:50.08,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,This shocking revelation was \N the hottest topic yesterday!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.09,0:06:06.18,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Melmetal, let’s keep twirling!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.31,0:06:16.23,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,There’s immense centrifugal force \N behind Melmetal’s fists-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Fire! Double Panzer!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.00,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Both its speed and its force \N have never been greater-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.46,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s the spirit, Melmetal!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.93,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Did you all see that? \N Wasn’t that an awesome punch?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.68,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What a shocker!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.93,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I could feel its immense power!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.14,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,You’ve got this, Melmetal!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.85,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,So strong! You can win!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.85,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It shook me, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.19,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Man, I can’t wait to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.82,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You get to battle Gaogaen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.82,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s show the Professor and Gaogaen \N how much stronger you’ve gotten!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.34,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! Now it’s Nyaheat’s turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.65,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,I’m a failure as a fan, aren’t I?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.78,0:07:48.74,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,I was so close to you, \N and yet I never noticed!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.91,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Royal Mask... \N No, Professor Kukui!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.87,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Give us a great battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.76,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Our apologies for the wait. \N It’s time for the exhibition match!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.76,0:08:13.10,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Royal Mask, a.k.a. Competitor Kukui, \N and Competitor Satoshi are entering the arena!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.11,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I’m super nervous for some reason!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.11,0:08:26.11,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Satoshi! You got this!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.25,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Kukui and \N Competitor Satoshi...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.25,0:08:46.13,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,...are slowly walking towards the middle, \N where Chief Referee Hala is waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.26,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Now allow me to \N go over the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.43,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,This will be a full battle.\N You may use six Pokémon each.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.52,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,You are free to switch out \N Pokémon mid-battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.52,0:09:06.15,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,The battle ends as soon as \N all Pokémon on one side are unable to battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.15,0:09:09.53,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,He who still has Pokémon left, wins.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.78,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,I expect a great battle from you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.79,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Both fighters, assume positions!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.12,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.50,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.55,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,It’s time!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.01,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Give it all you have!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.68,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Satoshi and Pikachu can win, \N for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.06,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,He’s got a great look on his face.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.48,0:09:45.40,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Satoshi now sends \N A heated wind that races \N Throughout Alola
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.19,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,There’s the Pokémon haiku!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.32,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Everyone, turn your attention \N to the screen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.95,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,It will display the status of each fighter’s \N six Pokémon for this full battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.95,0:09:58.70,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,It’ll help us keep track \N of the battle’s progress.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.83,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I already know who I’ll use first!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.96,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, Pikachu. Not you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You come in later.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.59,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat! I choose you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.10,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Nyabi-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.60,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I knew you’d use Nyaheat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.14,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Then I’ll use...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.07,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.65,0:10:35.03,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,There it is! Royal Mask’s \N strongest partner...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.16,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,His ace hits the scene!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.20,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,When he says Royal Mask, \N that’s Kukui{honorific note: Kukui-kun}, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.16,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Oh, I’m so glad I married him!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.13,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Gaogaen is Nyaheat’s \N evolved form.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.75,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,So that’s Nyabi-chan versus Gao-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.42,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,It’s time for a showdown \N between Fire Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.76,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,What kind of battle will this be?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat’s brimming with fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.68,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Yeah! Nyaheat’s emotions \N are swelling!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.32,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Fire power rising! Rising!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.21,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Let the battle begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.17,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Bring it, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.22,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go at full power, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.09,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.35,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Gaogaen, take them on! \N Build Up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.53,0:12:00.49,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,W-Wow! Build Up is a move that \N raises the user’s attack and defense!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.83,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,It used its bulging muscles \N to repel Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.83,0:12:07.54,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Gaogaen did not move an inch!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.04,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,I see... It is well trained!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.05,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.80,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s like a wall.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat, use another Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.31,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Another Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! Faster!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.10,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,So quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.69,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.57,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Nitro Charge raises the user’s speed \N every time it’s used-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.70,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,DD Lariat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.12,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,They dodged it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.29,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.38,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Raising his speed paid off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.50,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Fire Fang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.21,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Too soft!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.81,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We’re not done yet! \N Another Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.49,0:13:21.82,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon!{\i0}
Comment: 10,0:13:23.49,0:13:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.33,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.96,0:13:33.25,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We’re not done yet! \N Another Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.59,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Could Satoshi be...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.59,0:13:44.60,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Yeah. He’s planning to \N raise Nyaheat’s speed to the limit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.89,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Nyaheat’s speed \N continues to rise-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.89,0:13:50.98,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Round and round! \N Run circles around Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.74,0:14:05.74,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Nyaheat is quick! \N Gaogaen is stuck in place!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.87,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You’ve raised him well, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.25,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hell Thrust!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.34,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Charge in, Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Great Blaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.44,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,So strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.44,0:14:42.40,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You wanted to disorient Gaogaen \N by raising your speed with Nitro Charge, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.41,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.53,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,It regularly battles \N multiple opponents at once,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.70,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,so it can discern a Pokémon’s \N movements from any direction!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.25,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Gaogaen has no blind spots!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.76,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I’ll show you the heat of true fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.97,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Blast Burn!{Kalos flashbacks intensify. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.81,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,So hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.36,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It’s like being in the kitchen!{Huh. Blast Burn can’t be all that bad, then :| -StarfishI mean tbf they're not in the battlefield and they can still feel it so it's probably pretty darn hot. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.12,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.62,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.47,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I got it, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.39,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You’re taking in \N the Blast Burn fires, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.02,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s try that plan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.69,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.41,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Is this even possible?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.83,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,What could have happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.83,0:16:22.67,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Gaogaen’s Blast Burn \N vanished without a trace!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.13,0:16:26.05,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,What could have happened \N to Nyabi-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.51,0:16:30.80,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,He most likely absorbed \N all the flames from the Blast Burn.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.85,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,So that he could convert them \N into his own power.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.06,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,He can do that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.81,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Nyaheat’s body...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.85,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,...is on the brink of overflowing \N with fire energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.94,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,I’m certain it’s burning hotter \N by the second.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.57,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Nyabi-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,The power-up was a success, \N huh, Nyaheat?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,How’s that, Professor?! \N I call it Blast Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.84,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Now we can beat Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.46,0:17:11.22,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Blast Nyaheat, huh? \N You have the wildest ideas!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.72,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.10,0:17:19.02,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,The flames haven’t vanished. \N They only continue to blaze up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.65,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Blast Nyaheat! So cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.65,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,There’s no Pokémon \N with that name-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.86,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Just go with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.36,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.11,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I’d prefer “Nyaburn.”{I mean, that actually feels more in line with Nyabby and Nyaheat than “Gaogaen” does... -StarfishI love Suiren’s expression in this shot --PutoSame. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.95,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m not so sure about that...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.58,0:17:41.21,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,What is happening?! \N Smoke is rising from Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.54,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,He got burned!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.21,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,His bell got too hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.63,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,He couldn’t endure it, I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.51,0:17:55.35,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Too bad, Satoshi, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.64,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,That means you’re not ready \N to take in our Blast Burn just yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.95,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.16,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Return for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.38,0:18:32.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Your plan will work, no doubt!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.47,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I promise to give you a chance later!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.51,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,check move name,Guess we’ll have to Quash{sakiokuri / さきおくり} \N settling the score with Nyaheat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.93,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,But Gaogaen will stay in the fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.15,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,In that case, \N I’ll go with this guy next!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.53,0:18:53.53,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi’s second Pokémon \N is Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.28,0:18:59.37,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,After you use Blast Burn, \N you can’t move for a bit-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.08,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Do your best, Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.08,0:19:03.50,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,He’s got an advantage \N against Fire types!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.29,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,But his opponent is \N Royal Mask’s Gaogaen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.96,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,It won’t be easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.92,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s do this! Accel Rock!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.30,0:19:20.18,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Lugarugan goes in! \N Gaogaen still can’t move!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.85,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Stone Edge!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.94,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,They’re keeping up the pressure!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.11,0:19:31.44,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Oh! Gaogaen is back in action!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.07,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,DD Lariat!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.57,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.49,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lugarugan! Use the shards!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.37,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hell Thrust!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.79,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.39,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Good! You got them!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.40,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.27,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Even though his Stone Edge \N was shattered,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.27,0:20:14.03,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi used its shards! \N An inspired idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.90,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,And Lugarugan pulled through!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.90,0:20:21.24,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Their superb combination \N managed to damage Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.54,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Impressive, Lugarugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.08,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,All right, Gaogaen. \N Return for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.80,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You did it, Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.52,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi, let’s keep up \N the full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.07,0:21:02.20,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,It’s like you’ve gone back \N to your childhood self.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.58,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Go, Warrgle!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.38,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,check,It’s all on you, Warrgle!{it's all on you for this tanomu feels unideal because it feels a bit high-stakes for the (near) start of the fight -Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.38,0:21:16.63,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Kukui{honorific note: Kukui-kun}, show them \N how cool you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.76,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Warrgle, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.85,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi, \N will you switch your Pokémon?{wording lifted from the game, just because --Puto}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll stick with Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.77,0:21:32.27,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Very well. \N Then, let the battle begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.02,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Kukui uses Warrgle!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.02,0:21:40.20,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi, meanwhile, \N is leaving Lugarugan in!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.95,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Warrgle, use Rock Slide!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.70,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.20,0:21:53.17,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Alola Pokémon League exhibition match: \N Satoshi versus Kukui!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.17,0:21:57.67,Main,Narrator,0,750,0,,The battle has only begun. \N It’ll only heat up from here!
Comment: 10,0:21:59.46,0:21:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 10,0:23:20.46,0:23:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.09,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Battling’s intense!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.09,0:23:28.93,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,The first Pokémon Professor Kukui \N sent out was Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.93,0:23:33.52,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Warrgle versus Lugarugan... \N I wonder what kind of battle this’ll be!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.52,0:23:37.19,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,The Valiant Pokémon Warrgle \N is a Normal/Flying type!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.19,0:23:41.98,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Ancient Alolan people respected it, \N referring to it as “the hero of the sky.” {Sun Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.95,0:23:48.53,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Oh, my! That Warr-chan \N sure looks strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.24,0:23:54.25,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Warrgle spins around \N Dancing in the sky above \N A proud warrior
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.25,0:23:56.33,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.88,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Luga-chan! Hang in there!
Comment: 10,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.09,0:24:06.01,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Kukui{honorific note: Kukui-kun} is Royal Mask... \N I didn’t have two princes after all; only one!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.01,0:24:06.93,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,I’m a bit conflicted.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.64,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,There’s no time for that, \N Professor Burnet!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.64,0:24:10.51,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Sauboh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.51,0:24:15.10,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,I have started a petition \N to ensure that Royal Mask...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.10,0:24:18.94,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,...will continue to operate despite \N his identity being exposed! Sign, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.94,0:24:20.15,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Oh, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.15,0:24:22.69,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.07,0:24:25.49,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,A Flaming, Seething Full Battle!!!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.49,0:24:28.49,Main,Burnet & Sauboh,0,0,0,,Royal Mask will never die!
