Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.56,0:01:28.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:28.99,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\be3\bord9}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.99,0:01:35.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:35.28,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\be3\bord9}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.92,0:01:46.63,OP,,0,0,0,,You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:46.63,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.63,0:01:52.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:52.38,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25\be3\bord9}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.89,OP,,0,0,0,,Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.89,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.89,0:02:02.14,OP,,0,0,0,,will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:02.14,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.48,OP,,0,0,0,,Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.48,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.48,0:02:06.56,OP,,0,0,0,,playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:06.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.56,0:02:11.57,OP,,0,0,0,,go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:11.57,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.57,0:02:15.78,OP,,0,0,0,,You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:15.78,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.78,0:02:20.66,OP,,0,0,0,,how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:20.66,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.66,0:02:25.08,OP,,0,0,0,,Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:25.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.08,0:02:30.96,OP,,0,0,0,,Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:30.96,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.84,OP,,0,0,0,,Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.84,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.84,0:02:39.93,OP,,0,0,0,,With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:39.93,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.93,0:02:44.94,OP,,0,0,0,,It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:44.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.94,0:02:52.53,OP,,0,0,0,,Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:52.53,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:52.53,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=3}
